This sketch implements a Pump control via BT, serial port and push-button
It's developed for ESP32_ProgTherm v11 board
The BT classic takes the same command of Serial port but the printed messages are less (only GetStatus response)
pushbutton pin is on IO13 (Touch main)
Serial baudrate is 115200

Commands:
-help       // to show help menu
-Pump on    //turn on pump control
-Pump off   //turn off pump control
-GetStat    //read Pump control status
-reboot     //reboot ESP32
